</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Before warming up the engine</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<list1 type="nonmark">
<item>
<ptxt>When one of the following conditions is met:</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type="ordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Throttle valve opening angle is 1.5° or more.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Vehicle speed is 3 mph (5 km/h) or more.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Engine speed is 3,000 rpm or more.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>When the shift lever is in any position other than N.</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>After warming up the engine</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
