<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Engine coolant temp. is less than -10°C (14°F) or more than 60°C 140°F) or intake air temp. is less than -10°C (14°F).</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>OPEN</ptxt>
</entry>
